data.description: Located in the heart of the Karns community. This home is well kept in a small subdivision with pool and picnic access! Beautiful, level backyard with a 2-story workshop/shed. Lovely sunroom located off the kitchen and dining area with French doors leading out to the large deck area. Downstairs is a large bonus room and family room with a fireplace. From the family room, there is a hot tub room with a nice 6-person tub and terracotta tile floors with an exit to the covered patio. One year old 60 year metal roof.
